maintext:
MADISON, Wis. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Wednesday evening’s drawing of the Wisconsin Lottery’s “Daily Pick 4” game were:
6-1-7-0
(six, one, seven, zero)
¶ Maximum prize: $500
